        "scraping_time": "2024-05-27T11.00.22",
        "en_title": "Two thousand people buried by the land in Papua New Guinea",
        "en_content": "It's more than two thousand.\npeople who have been buried by a huge landslide,\na mountain in the night between Thursday and Friday in an area\nmountainous and almost inaccessible by Papua New Guinea. He did.\nPort Moresby release to the United Nations: \"The landslide\nmore than 2,000 people live and caused serious destruction,\" he said.\ndeclared the country's national disaster center at the office\nPort Moresby's Onu.\n\n\n\n\n\nReproduction reserved © Copyright ANSA\n\n\n\n",
